1
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,519
You brat!

2
00:00:22,239 --> 00:00:23,519
Out partying all day long.

3
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:25,519
Did you find the project I asked for?

4
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,839
Dad, there's still time, isn't there?

5
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:31,960
Besides, what does that kid even know?

6
00:00:32,560 --> 00:00:34,560
We'll just cook up some fake documents,

7
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:35,799
and fool him. Easy, right?

8
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:37,399
Him?

9
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:38,719
You think I care about him?

10
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:40,240
Sure, he's easy to fool,

11
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:41,600
but are the people behind him?

12
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:45,920
You ruin everything you touch.

13
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:53,439
And you?

14
00:00:55,039 --> 00:00:55,640
Grandpa,

15
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:58,399
I found this on the government website.

16
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,679
Would this work?

17
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:10,879
Yes, this is excellent.

18
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:13,760
However, I already called to check.

19
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:17,159
The Wang Family got this info too.

20
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:20,560
So their main partnership target

21
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,840
is likely still the Wang Family.

22
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,000
The Wang Family.

23
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:31,079
This way, miss.

24
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,480
Ruo Jin, you look lovely today.

25
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:36,159
Dad says he hasn't seen you in a while.

26
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,719
He wanted to invite you over.

27
00:01:42,159 --> 00:01:42,799
Hello, Uncle.

28
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,239
Ruo Jin,

29
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:45,680
it's been a long time.

30
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,480
Dad,

31
00:01:49,359 --> 00:01:50,040
recently,

32
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:53,000
there's a pharma museum project.

33
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,319
It's small, just over a million.

34
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:57,239
The upside is publicity for us,

35
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,239
and it gives us an endorsement.

36
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:01,599
It's a government exclusive partnership.

37
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,120
Exclusive endorsement brings Credibility.

38
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,800
Ruo Jin's here.

39
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,479
You're still talking business?

40
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,560
Ruo Jin's practically family.

41
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,280
Besides, the company's future affairs,

42
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,479
shouldn't Ruo Jin know about them too?

43
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,199
Alright.

44
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,759
A small project like this, you handle it.

45
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,680
Okay.

46
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,560
Alright, show him in.

47
00:02:31,439 --> 00:02:33,800
Take Ruo Jin inside first.

48
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,199
I've got a visitor.

49
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,080
Okay.

50
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:38,240
Ruo Jin.

51
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:54,120
It's been so long since we've caught up.

52
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,960
So today, these old bones

53
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,879
came to visit Chairman Wang in person.

54
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,919
Elder Li, please don't say that.

55
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:05,719
Company matters have been hectic lately.

56
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,280
I just couldn't get away.

57
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,719
As busy as you are,

58
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,960
you're not just here for a visit, are you?

59
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:12,759
You're right.

60
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,439
There's something I'd like to discuss.

61
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:25,400
Why are you taking my things?

62
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:27,719
You won't share, so I'll just take it.

63
00:03:29,159 --> 00:03:30,719
Give the ball back to Yixin, now.

64
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:31,599
Give it back to her!

65
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,680
My dad said

66
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,599
no one is allowed to bully me.

67
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:36,840
Go cry to your daddy then, if you can!

68
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,039
Little brat!

69
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:45,199
Daddy, Daddy!

70
00:03:45,199 --> 00:03:46,599
She's bullying me.

71
00:03:48,479 --> 00:03:49,280
Are you okay, son?

72
00:03:50,159 --> 00:03:52,639
Daddy, Daddy, she bullied me!

73
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,680
You little snot-nosed brat,

74
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,000
how dare you bully my son!

75
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:56,319
I'll...

76
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,319
Dad.

77
00:04:11,439 --> 00:04:13,759
Your son clearly grabbed her things first.

78
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:16,000
Not sorting out the facts is one thing,

79
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:18,079
but how dare you lay hands on a child?

80
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,360
You...

81
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,160
You just wait!

82
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,519
Anytime you want.

83
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,279
Let's go, son.

84
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,000
Come on.

85
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:27,720
Bah!

86
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,600
Scumbag!

87
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:30,839
Are you okay?

88
00:04:33,639 --> 00:04:34,720
Yixin, are you hurt?

89
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:36,439
Honestly,

90
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,360
how could you leave a child here alone?

91
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,160
She was about to get slapped!

92
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,600
Do you know how serious that could be?

93
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,279
I just really needed the restroom,

94
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:45,120
and since Yixin knows Junjun,

95
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,439
I didn't take her with me.

96
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,560
You okay?

97
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:56,120
This means nothing to the Wang Family.

98
00:04:56,519 --> 00:04:58,199
But as you know,

99
00:04:58,399 --> 00:05:00,439
Wenhao just recently

100
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:02,319
signed a deal with Jingteng Corporation.

101
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:05,920
Jingteng Corporation values backgrounds.

102
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,600
Any company with government-backed projects

103
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,759
gets priority investment from them.

104
00:05:11,439 --> 00:05:16,079
It's also an exclusive partnership.

105
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:19,279
The Wang Family has government projects!

106
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,199
I only need this one small project.

107
00:05:24,439 --> 00:05:25,040
Elder Li,

108
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,439
please don't rush this.

109
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,720
Send the project files over to me first.

110
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:31,000
However,

111
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:33,519
I'll need to discuss it further.

112
00:05:34,439 --> 00:05:36,800
If you really insist on joining in,

113
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,879
why don't our two families do it together?

114
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:42,240
No, I want an exclusive partnership.

115
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:49,000
Someone!

116
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,480
Show him out.

117
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:04,720
Grandpa threw a fit after coming home.

118
00:06:05,439 --> 00:06:06,720
Just as you predicted,

119
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,399
Wang Chengren turned him down.

120
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:13,240
Wang Chengren is suspicious by nature.

121
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,000
Your Grandpa showing up at his door

122
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:17,720
with a project he wouldn't care about—

123
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,399
of course he'd be suspicious.

124
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,519
So what's your next move?

125
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:28,720
Set up another meeting with Grandpa soon.

126
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,399
Then spread the word

127
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:32,240
that Li Family will get the Wanli Pill.

128
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,160
Here's the contract.

129
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,519
Feifan,

130
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:48,600
after this whole thing is over,

131
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:51,519
are you planning to never see me again?

132
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,439
Will you really not even consider me?

133
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:09,240
I'll not only be your friend,

134
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,240
but also your strongest ally.

135
00:07:14,439 --> 00:07:15,759
Most importantly,

136
00:07:18,519 --> 00:07:20,360
I'll be completely honest with you.

137
00:07:55,279 --> 00:07:56,160
What are you doing here?

138
00:07:59,120 --> 00:07:59,600
What?

139
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,319
Am I interrupting something?

140
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,959
I need to talk to you.

141
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:04,600
Xu Ruo Jin.

142
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:08,360
I never knew you had this hobby.

143
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,839
You followed me?

144
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,759
Yes.

145
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,759
I did follow you.

146
00:08:16,839 --> 00:08:18,160
I looked for you at Kui Medical Hall.

147
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,360
I saw you just heading out,

148
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,600
so I had to follow you all the way here.

149
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,000
Why look for me at Kui Medical Hall?

150
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:28,160
I went to the Wang Family today,

151
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,560
and saw Li Qiankun meet Wang Chengren.

152
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:34,799
The Wang Family is also planning

153
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:37,000
a government pharma museum project.

154
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,000
I know.

155
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:41,240
You know?

156
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:52,720
So you and Shen Yue are busy with this.

157
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,519
I was sticking my nose where it didn't belong.

158
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,679
Xu Ruo Jin.

159
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,360
Get this straight.

160
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,679
We're history.

161
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:08,879
You're Wang Wenhao's fiancee now.

162
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,639
I will take revenge on the Wang Family.

163
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,039
So no matter what,

164
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:20,000
please stay away from me.
